</math>


And finally multiply:


<math>
G =

\begin{array} {ccc}
\mathrm{T}C(M\mathrm{T}C)^\mathsf{T}(M\mathrm{T}C(M\mathrm{T}C)^\mathsf{T})^{-1} \\
\left[ \begin{array} {rrr}
{-0.147066} \\
